### Health
GET http://localhost:4004/health

### Upload a receipt (PDF)
POST http://localhost:4004/api/receipts/upload
x-api-key: mylocaldevkey
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

--WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="clientId"

acme
--WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="posId"

POS-42
--WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="dateISO"

2025-08-31
--WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="receipt.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
--WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Generate expiring SAS (read-only for 15 minutes)
POST http://localhost:4004/api/receipts/signed-url
x-api-key: mylocaldevkey
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blobPath": "client/acme/2025/08/31/POS-42/abc-123.pdf",
  "permissions": "r",
  "expirySeconds": 900
}

### Generate permanent SAS (revocable by policy)
POST http://localhost:4004/api/receipts/signed-url
x-api-key: mylocaldevkey
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blobPath": "client/acme/2025/08/31/POS-42/abc-123.pdf",
  "permanent": true
}

### Fetch metadata & tags
GET http://localhost:4004/api/receipts/info?blobPath=client/acme/2025/08/31/POS-42/abc-123.pdf
x-api-key: mylocaldevkey

### Stream download
GET http://localhost:4004/api/receipts/download?blobPath=client/acme/2025/08/31/POS-42/abc-123.pdf&attachment=false
